snippet.title: Weibenfalk
snippet.description:
I'm Thomas Weibenfalk. A developer and designer from Sweden.

I share my knowledge of modern front end development in a (hopefully) down to earth and fun way!

I'll cover topics as React, Vanilla Javascript, Gatsby, CSS, HTML and occasional backend development. A lot of the focus is on ReactJS cause I love it! As I'm also a designer there might even be some UI/UX stuff from time to time.

This channel is for both beginner and experienced Front End developers who wants to learn more.

So ... if you want to learn the latest in Front End this is the channel for you to subscribe to. ;)
